com.example.bookmark.server

Class InMemoryStorageService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.bookmark.server.InMemoryStorageService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StorageService

    public class InMemoryStorageService
extends java.lang.Object
implements StorageService
    An implementation of StorageProvider that stores all of the app's data in memory. Useful for intent testing and other types of tests that do not need a server connection.
